artiesPolviews,\n  aes(\n    x = partyidRecode,\n    fill = polviewsRecode\n  )\n) +\n  geom_bar(\n    position = 'fill',\n    stat = 'bin'\n  ) +\n  scale_y_continuous(\n    labels = percent_format()\n  ) +\n  facet_grid(decade ~ partyidRecode) + \n  coord_polar(theta = 'y') \n  \n\n\n",
